msgstr "Post your material on third-party sites"

# 4482bc604bb449a9bcc5151b0c59a6cd
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:46
msgid ""
"Many blogs have created a large readership in specialised topic areas. It "
"may be worthwhile adding an article about your initative on their site. "
"These can be mutually beneficial. You receive more interest and they receive"
" a free blog post in their topic area."
msgstr "Viele Blogs haben eine große Reichweite bei bestimmten Themen. Versuchen Sie, einen Artikel über Ihre Initiative dort zu platzieren."

# 4e521921a7a741bebd036b1131279a22
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:53
msgid "Making your communications more social-media friendly"
msgstr "Machen Sie ihre Kommunikation 'social media freundlich'"

# 2e4a77be81a645de990cdf3bd4c53138
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:55
msgid ""
"It's unrealistic to expect that officials should spend large periods of time"
" engaging with social media. However, there are several things that you can "
"do to make sure that your content can be easily shared between technical "
"users."
msgstr "Auch wenn es unrealistisch scheint, dass Beamte und andere Behördenmitarbeiter viel Zeit in sozialen Netzwerken verbringen gibt es ein paar einfache Tipps wie Sie sicherstellen können das Ihre Informationen leicht in solchen Netzwerken weiterverbreitet werden können."

# 66929f4b84a148938f8e5dcd5f98db9b
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:60
msgid "Some tips:"
msgstr "Ein paar Tipps:"

# 06a1a7384f5248159bee0aa610ef1b08
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:62
msgid ""
"Provide unique pages for each piece of content When a message is shared with"
" others, the recipient of the referral will be looking for the relevant "
"content quickly."
msgstr "Legen Sie für alle Inhalte eigene Seiten an. Dies erleichtert die Verlinkung und erreichbarkeit Ihrer Informationen."

# e60e95c014554dc1bbcf5acc118621ee
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:66
msgid ""
"Avoid making people download your press releases Press releases are fine. "
"They are concise messages about a particular point. However, if you require "
"people to download the content and for it to open outside of a web browser, "
"then fewer people will read it. Search engines are less likely to index the "
"content. People are less likely to click to download."
msgstr "Vermeiden Sie, Informationen nur zum Download anzubieten. Viele Leute werden sich Informationen nicht konsumieren, die Sie extra herunterladen müssen um sie außerhalb des Browsers anzuschauen. Ausserdem können solche Informationen schlechter von Suchmaschinen indiziert werden, und somit schwerer gefunden werden."

# d194d73de8e34ba9b51969b94cd4bad4
#: following-up/tell-the-world.rst:73
msgid ""
"Consider using a Creative Commons licence Apart from providing certainty to "
